AS CAUTIONARY TALE,
SEX AS A WARNING.

14:54.083 --> 14:55.417
I'M NOT KIDDING
ABOUT THIS.

14:55.417 --> 14:56.917
EVERY TIME SOMEBODY
IN ONE OF THOSE BOOKS
HAS SEX,

14:56.917 --> 14:59.417
