BY IT, HE POKES OUT
HIS OWN EYES.

15:16.834 --> 15:19.250
OK? THAT'S
NOT REAL LIFE.

15:19.250 --> 15:22.959
CORRECT ME IF I'M WRONG,
BUT IT HAS BEEN
KNOWN TO HAPPEN

15:22.959 --> 15:26.166
THAT EVERY ONCE IN
A WHILE, TWO PEOPLE
SLEEP TOGETHER,

15:26.166 --> 15:29.750
THEY ENJOY IT, AND
AFTERWARD, EVERYTHING
WORKS OUT FINE.

15:29.750 --> 15:33.333
YOU REALLY THINK
THAT IS POSSIBLE?

15:48.458 --> 15:49.583
STEVEN?

15:49.583 --> 15:51.583
RAHHRRR!

15:51.583 --> 15:53.750
AAH!

15:56.291 --> 16:00.291
