16:34.250 --> 16:35.959
WHY ARE YOU
SO SURPRISED

16:35.959 --> 16:39.333
EVERY TIME I JUMP
AT THE CHANCE TO
SPEND TIME WITH YOU?

16:39.333 --> 16:42.500
