JUST DISPLACED ANGER,

39:03.625 --> 39:05.000
AND YOU'RE MAD
AT YOUR MOM AND DAD.

39:05.000 --> 39:06.875
I'M MAD AT THE WORLD,
JOEY.

39:06.875 --> 39:08.333
I'M A TEENAGER.

39:08.333 --> 39:09.792
OH, AND BY THE WAY,
WE'RE OLD PALS NOW,
BLONDIE AND I,

39:09.792 --> 39:13.792
SO, UH, YOU HAVE ANY MESSAGES
YOU WANT TO GET BACK TO HER,

39:13.792 --> 39:14.792
JUST LET ME KNOW--

39:14.792 --> 39:16.166
LOOK, JOEY, WHATEVER
YOU'VE DONE, THANKS,

39:16.166 --> 39:18.625
BUT I JUST DON'T
WANT TO TALK ABOUT IT
RIGHT NOW.

39:18.625 --> 39:20.375
WITH YOU.

39:20.375 --> 39:21.333
COME ON.

39:21.333 --> 39:22.834
PASSING UP A CHANCE

39:22.834 --> 39:26.000
TO DISH ABOUT
THE GIRL OF YOUR DREAMS?

39:26.000 --> 39:27.500
I THOUGHT THAT'S WHAT
YOU DID WITH YOUR FRIENDS.

39:27.500 --> 39:30.500
IT IS, EXCEPT I'M
NOT SURE THAT WE ARE.

39:33.750 --> 39:34.959
OH.

39:36.041 --> 39:37.667
HOW DROLL.

39:37.667 --> 39:39.542
THE TABLES
HAVE BEEN TURNED.

39:39.542 --> 39:41.417
THIS ISN'T JUST
ABOUT YESTERDAY, JOEY.

39:41.417 --> 39:42.500
IT'S LAST WEEK,
LAST MONTH.

39:42.500 --> 39:45.959
IT...EVERYTHING
BETWEEN US RECENTLY.

39:45.959 --> 39:47.500
WE JUST...

39:47.500 --> 39:50.125
WE'RE NOT GETTING ALONG
THE SAME WAY WE USED TO.

39:50.125 --> 39:51.083
SO THE FRIENDSHIP,

39:51.083 --> 39:53.917
YOU DON'T THINK
WE'RE FRIENDS ANYMORE?

39:53.917 --> 39:56.583
OH, I DON'T...

39:56.583 --> 39:58.917
I DON'T KNOW. ARE WE
MORE? ARE WE LESS?

39:58.917 --> 40:04.041
I...ALL I KNOW IS,
IT'S JUST NOT THE WAY
IT USED TO BE.

40:04.041 --> 40:05.500
NOTHING IS ANYMORE.

40:05.500 --> 40:09.208
IT'S CALLED SOCIAL EVOLUTION,
DAWSON.

40:09.208 --> 40:10.875
WHAT'S STRONG ENOUGH
FLOURISHES,

40:10.875 --> 40:15.041
AND WHAT DOESN'T WE
LOOK AT BEHIND GLASS CASES
IN SCIENCE MUSEUMS.

40:16.542 --> 40:18.125
YOU AND I?

40:19.542 --> 40:22.458
ARE WE MUSEUM-BOUND?

40:23.959 --> 40:25.834
I DON'T KNOW ABOUT THAT.

40:31.000 --> 40:33.083
YOU GET ANGRY AT ME
TOO EASILY.

40:33.083 --> 40:35.125
YOU'RE WAY
TOO CRITICAL OF ME.

40:38.625 --> 40:40.792
YOU KNOW, IN SOME
ALTERNATE UNIVERSE,

40:40.792 --> 40:42.542
WE MUST HAVE BEEN
MARRIED, LIKE, 50 YEARS.

40:42.542 --> 40:44.041
YEAH, AND I'M SURE IT WAS
A WONDERFUL WEDDING.

40:44.041 --> 40:45.917
OH, THE BEST.

40:45.917 --> 40:46.875
WE EACH BROUGHT DATES,
I ASSUME.

40:46.875 --> 40:49.875
YEAH, JEN WAS
BY MY SIDE THROUGHOUT.

40:49.875 --> 40:53.750
AND AT THE END OF THE EVENING,
THE INEVITABLE QUESTION.

40:53.750 --> 40:55.375
WHO DO YOU TAKE HOME?

40:55.375 --> 40:57.166
THE DATE OR THE WIFE?

40:57.166 --> 40:58.792
MMM. A DILEMMA.

40:58.792 --> 41:00.125
BUT FASCINATING.

41:00.125 --> 41:04.000
FACED WITH THE CHOICE,
YOU STOOD, SURVEYING
YOUR OPTIONS.

41:04.000 --> 41:09.500
YOUR EYES DRIFTED SLOWLY...
FROM HER...TO ME...

41:10.250 --> 41:11.792
THEN BACK TO HER...

41:14.500 --> 41:16.458
THEN BACK TO YOU?

41:16.458 --> 41:20.125
YEAH, BUT I WAS OFF
HAVING A DRINK WITH
THE RICH GUY AT THE BAR.

41:20.125 --> 41:21.125
UNTIL MONEYBAGS
GOT FRESH,

41:21.125 --> 41:23.875
AND YOU NEEDED SOMEBODY
TO BAIL YOU OUT.

41:23.875 --> 41:24.875
REALLY?

41:24.875 --> 41:25.834
MM-HMM.

41:25.834 --> 41:27.291
I DON'T REMEMBER THAT PART.

41:27.291 --> 41:28.917
OH, I DO, CLEAR AS DAY,
ABSOLUTELY.

41:28.917 --> 41:33.125
YOU...WERE DEFINITELY
IN NEED OF A RESCUE.

41:33.125 --> 41:34.708
AND WERE YOU MAN ENOUGH?

41:34.708 --> 41:40.166
DID YOU SET ASIDE
YOUR CLEARHEADED ANALYSIS
OF THE SITUATION AND ACT?

41:44.667 --> 41:47.625
DID WE, UH, DID WE SAVE
EACH OTHER THAT NIGHT,
DAWSON?

41:54.583 --> 41:58.792
I--YOU KNOW, IT GETS
SO HAZY AT THIS POINT,

41:58.792 --> 42:01.000
I--I REALLY
CAN'T REMEMBER.

42:01.000 --> 42:02.583
COULDN'T TELL YA.

42:02.583 --> 42:05.917
WELL, WHEN IT COMES
BACK TO YOU,

42:05.917 --> 42:10.500
I'D CERTAINLY BE CURIOUS
TO HEAR HOW IT ALL ENDED.

42:10.500 --> 42:12.375
YOU'LL BE MY FIRST CALL.

42:21.208 --> 42:23.500
WELL...GOOD NIGHT, DAWSON.

42:23.500 --> 42:26.875
ALL THIS SUBTEXT
IS MAKING ME TIRED.

42:32.875 --> 42:34.291
DAWSON?

42:34.291 --> 42:36.792
YEAH?

42:39.542 --> 42:42.000
NO MATTER HOW
THE WEDDING TURNED OUT...

42:44.375 --> 42:48.041
I'M PRETTY SURE
I HAD A WONDERFUL TIME
UP UNTIL THE END.

42:48.041 --> 42:50.125
YEAH.

42:54.166 --> 42:55.750
ME, TOO.

43:11.250 --> 43:12.708
NO DOUBT ABOUT IT.

43:14.667 --> 43:17.291
STRAIGHT
TO THE SMITHSONIAN.
